text: Michael Ann was the perfect host.  She made you feel right at home the minute you arrived.  Her apartment was adorable and very clean.  The location is great, on  a lovely quiet street. Everything you could possibly need for an enjoyable stay was provided.  And, if you have any questions she  is very accessible. If you are looking for that special place to stay in Austin this is it.
title: Beautiful Backyard Garage Apartment
